<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <title>교육원 가격비교</title>
</head>
<body>
{{>layout/header}}

<main class="comparison-container">
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>교육원 가격비교</h1>
        <p>다양한 교육원의 가격을 비교해보세요</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 목록 출력 영역 -->
    <div class="table-container">
        <table class="comparison-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th class="id-column">번호</th>
                    <th class="title-column">교육원명 및 과정</th>
                    <th class="author-column">작성자</th>
                    <th class="date-column">등록일</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#posts}}
                <tr class="table-row">
                    <td class="id-cell">{{id}}</td>
                    <td class="title-cell">
                        <a href="/posts/view/{{id}}" class="post-link">{{title}}</a>
                    </td>
                    <td class="author-cell">{{author}}</td>
                    <td class="date-cell">{{modifiedDate}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/posts}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="/posts/save" class="btn btn-primary">새 가격정보 등록</a>
    </div>
</main>

{{>layout/footer}}
</body>
</html>
